        "subject": "LU-3450 build: Increase ldiskfs version to 3.3.6",
        "message": "LU-3450 build: Increase ldiskfs version to 3.3.6\n\nThe ldiskfs version number has not changed in quite some time.\nThis brings the versioning up-to-date to allow upgrade to require\nproper dependency.\nAdd an explicit requirement for \"lustre-backend-fs >= 3.3.6\"\nto the lustre spec file at the same time.\n\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <minh.diep@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I8d84f5c505b99346085cc991d07e15ce1fc5888e\n"
